{"tid":2421880,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–降膽固醇藥","createTime":"2021-02-24T23:17:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T21:33:50.000Z","uid":38861,"like":56,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ed40964d378933e7fb0773f9b14d463f3ae8371e","tid":2421880,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T23:17:02.000Z","msg":"油並無法容易溶於水裡，因此當脂肪從我們身體的血液循環系統時，便需要依靠蛋白質的輔助，合體成為脂蛋白(Lipoprotein)，才能方便於血液中流動行走。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RqscWGj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRqscWGj.jpg&h=ce4bf258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖2）根據密度及體積，脂蛋白可分成為不同種類。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPuOu1o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPuOu1o.jpg&h=945ede61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLow Density Lipoprotein(LDL)主要負責從肝臟把油脂傳送到各器官，而血液LDL含量長期高企的話，患上心臟病或中風的機會亦會高企，因此經常被冠稱為壞膽固醇。<br />\n<br />\n而當細胞尤其是肝臟細胞內的膽固醇過多的話，便會以High Density Lipoprotein(HDL)的形式排出細胞外。<br />\n細胞內含有過多膽固醇的話便會觸發細胞進行死亡的機制，基於HDL能把它們帶出細胞外，避免壞事發生，因此亦被稱之為好膽固醇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）細胞可從外間直接攝取膽固醇，又或者是從其他原料自行製作膽固醇。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gVK6077.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgVK6077.png&h=44d99665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n降膽固醇藥Statin能夠抑制其中一隻參與製作膽固醇過程的酶素，導致膽固醇的製作無法順利完成。<br />\n<br />\n而細胞在藥物的誤導下，以為是自己因為吸收不足夠的LDL，所以無法製作膽固醇，因此便會增大吸收外間LDL的能力，得出的結果就是把血液裡的壞膽固醇含量大幅度下降。<br />\n<br />\n能降低血液LDL含量固然是一件好事，畢竟血液LDL含量與心臟病中風等疾病有著密切的關聯。<br />\n但亦有一些統計數據指出服用Statin會增加患癌風險，其機制現時尚未能搞得清楚。<br />\n<br />\nStatin藥物所抑制的製作膽固醇的機制，箇中亦包含其他有用的有機物及代謝物製作。<br />\n干涉到那些有機物的製作會否促成癌症生長，還需要大量的研究作出探討。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8HHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=59ada17f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8HHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=1da9e006\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8561503/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F8561503%2F&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8HHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=a3dc8ee8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8561503/</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC7225778/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC7225778%2F&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8HHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=7ed09979\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC7225778/</a>"},{"pid":"5164344076cd746b10cab88846110b2b50cd5865","tid":2421880,"uid":49588,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T23:20:02.000Z","msg":"有水準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3cb43b3725d392f46d4a57ff8d7aad99f5406c","tid":2421880,"uid":54323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T23:37:45.000Z","msg":"點預防高膽固醇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef80cf78012fbf478c67847d194756bf7461cd8d","tid":2421880,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T23:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc499f13c3b681d8c946c3ce8a82f6416d19d7e1","tid":2421880,"uid":389598,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T00:06:28.000Z","msg":"支持樓主<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0c8dfd0327c4ba1161c709e1712ef1c71b3c53","tid":2421880,"uid":64720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T00:10:51.000Z","msg":"咁多隻statin有咩分別"},{"pid":"aab7ff7898b92eab81dcfa0ba7633901f0e24939","tid":2421880,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T00:53:01.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"334b53dbeb43ee0bfeac1029cd379cb9dac84ca3","tid":2421880,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T00:55:31.000Z","msg":"咁啲藥既負作用勁唔勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b931963ad3deb79e113cccae7776df60368e0cca","tid":2421880,"uid":70007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T01:31:58.000Z","msg":"講下PCSK9 inhibitor?"},{"pid":"429412e248b87380be058c6ae41328547659a6d4","tid":2421880,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T01:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a67eca926cf839de70af2ebf56f0a5e127b620","tid":2421880,"uid":155238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e3cb43b3725d392f46d4a57ff8d7aad99f5406c","tid":2421880,"uid":54323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T23:37:45.000Z","msg":"點預防高膽固醇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T01:59:29.000Z","msg":"唔好食咁油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df895aaf938a174657c6517d4b4464695179e292","tid":2421880,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T02:01:01.000Z","msg":"點做先增加好膽固醇"},{"pid":"bacf227503b10be8b6c255a006bbd6b7c5eeda25","tid":2421880,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:36:52.000Z","msg":"咁講食藥後係咪血液內少咗LDL，去咗器官度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa58cade26c069e4465da876a9be5f4fd888d1b","tid":2421880,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:45:51.000Z","msg":"細胞吸曬啲LDL但又冇得整膽固醇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁會點"},{"pid":"268cdce5d23891310043e6d00f36aa075a3151fc","tid":2421880,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:51:15.000Z","msg":"其實可唔可以主動叫醫生開藥<br />\n如果心跳得好快 試過睇政府醫生<br />\n<br />\n佢都係叫我做運動同注意飲食"},{"pid":"8ee198b4cbc601556a7e5d40331d619bda5062bc","tid":2421880,"uid":379629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:52:53.000Z","msg":"細胞吸晒ldl咁咪好多脂肪囉<br />\n咁會以hdl(正常）定ldl（吸返黎）放返出血<br />\n同埋Hdl入左血點解唔會好似ldl咁塞血管<br />\n定身體有辨法排Hdl 出體外 而ldl唔得？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a00d0e78e1c3fad28b58f595b97743a011ee81","tid":2421880,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27a67eca926cf839de70af2ebf56f0a5e127b620","tid":2421880,"uid":155238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e3cb43b3725d392f46d4a57ff8d7aad99f5406c","tid":2421880,"uid":54323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T23:37:45.000Z","msg":"點預防高膽固醇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T01:59:29.000Z","msg":"唔好食咁油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:18:36.000Z","msg":"早餐長期食用燕麥片 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6847f9db061efa19e6e13f9456931dc13e0d8a81","tid":2421880,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bacf227503b10be8b6c255a006bbd6b7c5eeda25","tid":2421880,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:36:52.000Z","msg":"咁講食藥後係咪血液內少咗LDL，去咗器官度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:11:09.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e2c2c380075ac777255db8f2445a587c4f3766","tid":2421880,"uid":287289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b931963ad3deb79e113cccae7776df60368e0cca","tid":2421880,"uid":70007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T01:31:58.000Z","msg":"講下PCSK9 inhibitor?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:37:17.000Z","msg":"PCSK9 inhibitor 個MOA 重簡單過statin。原理就係PCSK9 protein 就會導致LDL receptor internalisation and degradation。 所以藥廠就用monoclonal antibody 做PCSK9 inhibitor，去減少active PCSK9 protein 係血液循環道，從而減少LDL receptor degradation。多左LDL receptor 未可以uptake 多啲LDL cholesterol 係血液循環入面，從而降低LDL cholesterol levels。 <br />\n<br />\n完。"},{"pid":"afaf36bfc43106941c131496c53bda0dc602257c","tid":2421880,"uid":265227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:39:18.000Z","msg":"咁食咗藥之後導致細胞吸收多咗LDL會唔會整死埋D細胞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3e74808bfa1e77bea97918c533730faa12eb95","tid":2421880,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0e2c2c380075ac777255db8f2445a587c4f3766","tid":2421880,"uid":287289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b931963ad3deb79e113cccae7776df60368e0cca","tid":2421880,"uid":70007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T01:31:58.000Z","msg":"講下PCSK9 inhibitor?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:37:17.000Z","msg":"PCSK9 inhibitor 個MOA 重簡單過statin。原理就係PCSK9 protein 就會導致LDL receptor internalisation and degradation。 所以藥廠就用monoclonal antibody 做PCSK9 inhibitor，去減少active PCSK9 protein 係血液循環道，從而減少LDL receptor degradation。多左LDL receptor 未可以uptake 多啲LDL cholesterol 係血液循環入面，從而降低LDL cholesterol levels。 <br />\n<br />\n完。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:47:12.000Z","msg":"Statin的原理其實都有少少相似，佢雖然最終令到LDLr的steady state level無變，但degradation rate其實快咗，亦即係最終代表LDLr吸收外間LDL的效率勁咗，減低血液的LDL。"},{"pid":"b4fb5480db6ffb832e72189c3eaab6765c87b702","tid":2421880,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afaf36bfc43106941c131496c53bda0dc602257c","tid":2421880,"uid":265227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:39:18.000Z","msg":"咁食咗藥之後導致細胞吸收多咗LDL會唔會整死埋D細胞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:48:31.000Z","msg":"其實應該就會，我都唔太清楚，但statin係有已知副作用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db3f7a9d1f424f15afbcbb64485a0f39b747535","tid":2421880,"uid":287289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"afaf36bfc43106941c131496c53bda0dc602257c","tid":2421880,"uid":265227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:39:18.000Z","msg":"咁食咗藥之後導致細胞吸收多咗LDL會唔會整死埋D細胞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:48:45.000Z","msg":"正常藥物劑量唔會令致啲細胞可以吸收過量大量LDL cholesterol 導致細胞死亡，相返太多LDL cholesterol 係血液中會導致oxidised LDL cholesterol 的產生，從而令macrophage 去吸收oxidised LDL cholesterol 去形成foam cells 導致動脈硬化。"},{"pid":"b6f3e3447c8b8e6e55daf58ac29c1de861c61443","tid":2421880,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0db3f7a9d1f424f15afbcbb64485a0f39b747535","tid":2421880,"uid":287289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"afaf36bfc43106941c131496c53bda0dc602257c","tid":2421880,"uid":265227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:39:18.000Z","msg":"咁食咗藥之後導致細胞吸收多咗LDL會唔會整死埋D細胞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:48:45.000Z","msg":"正常藥物劑量唔會令致啲細胞可以吸收過量大量LDL cholesterol 導致細胞死亡，相返太多LDL cholesterol 係血液中會導致oxidised LDL cholesterol 的產生，從而令macrophage 去吸收oxidised LDL cholesterol 去形成foam cells 導致動脈硬化。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:50:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"027118dbdfbb7e06aef25e4d2053c110fda703d5","tid":2421880,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6847f9db061efa19e6e13f9456931dc13e0d8a81","tid":2421880,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bacf227503b10be8b6c255a006bbd6b7c5eeda25","tid":2421880,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:36:52.000Z","msg":"咁講食藥後係咪血液內少咗LDL，去咗器官度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T07:11:09.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:56:43.00